c: 18
v: 14
t: "Kaadu ken (gablâ mara kinnuk) lubbittet iimaan diggi hayne korostah yan amoytih foocal soolen waqdi, tokkel kaal gacisak:ni- Rabbi Qaranwaa kee baaxô Rabbiiy nanu kaak-sa hebeltô Yalla manaqbuda, toysa nummah nanu tama maxcok kalih maxcot yabne nee tekkek caddok taturreeh diraabat yabne nee iyyen"